Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:05.12,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Attention, everypony! Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:08.39,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,The official Rainbow Dash\Nfan club will come to order.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.39,0:00:11.18,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Let's get right down to our\Nfirst order of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:16.05,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I motion that Rainbow Dash be declared\Nthe most awesome pony in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:17.61,Snails,,0,0,0,,I second the motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:21.67,Snails,,0,0,0,,And might I add that if you looked up\Nthe word "awesome" in the dictionary…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.67,0:00:23.61,Snails,,0,0,0,,…there would be\Na picture of Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:26.46,Snips,,0,0,0,,I object!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.27,0:00:30.58,Snips,,0,0,0,,I think the word\N"awesome" is played out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:32.55,Snips,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash deserves better.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:37.24,Snips,,0,0,0,,I motion that we declare her\Nthe most stupendous pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:39.89,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,"Stupendous"?\NIs that the best you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:42.17,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I motion that we declare her…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.24,0:00:43.92,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,…wonderrific!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:45.02,Snips,,0,0,0,,Astonishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:46.42,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Breathtaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:47.73,Snips,,0,0,0,,Astounding!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:49.11,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Bedazzling!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:52.23,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What about superultraextremawesomeazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.52,0:00:58.71,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,All in favor of declaring Rainbow Dash\Nthe most superultraextra…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:02.27,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,…uh, whatever you said,\Npony in all of Ponyville, say aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:03.33,Somepony,,0,0,0,,AYE!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:54.47,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:59.97,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,There's nothing like a dip in the clouds\Nto make a pegasus feel super-relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:02.38,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:05.28,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Help! Heeelp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.28,0:02:08.25,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Looks like my sky swim\Nwill have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.72,0:02:13.91,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm Rainbow Dash\Nand I'm here to rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:25.41,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Wow. What's with this crowd?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:29.13,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Uh… Thanks everypony. It was really no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:32.94,Somepony,,0,0,0,,To me it was.\NYou're my hero, Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:41.62,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,That Rainbow Dash sure is something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:44.19,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:25.50,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh no! There's something\Nwrong with the baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:32.03,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,She's not cheering for everypony's\Nfavorite hero: Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:50.77,Somepony,,0,0,0,,There just aren't enough words in the dictionary\Nto describe Rainbow Dash's awesomeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:52.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can think of a few new words.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:55.52,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And I bet "modest" is not one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:03.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No, but she is kinda awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:20.24,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Never fear, your friendly neighborhood\NRainbow Dash is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:33.90,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We'd be lost without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:36.15,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You're our hero, Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:38.71,Somepony,,0,0,0,,RAINBOW DASH! RAINBOW DASH!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:41.52,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:51.71,Somepony,,0,0,0,,RAINBOW DASH! RAINBOW DASH! RAINBOW DASH!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:56.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Call me silly, but I think this whole hero thing\Nmight be going to Rainbow Dash's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:04:59.05,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You may be right… silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:03.77,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And then I zoomed into the well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:07.64,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I knew it would be dark and dangerous,\Nbut I didn't let that stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:09.30,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Danger's my middle name:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.39,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Danger Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:15.42,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Thinking back on it, I acted pretty\Nawesomely heroic that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:17.27,Spike,,0,0,0,,"…that day."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:20.86,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Awesomely heroic that day and\Nawesomely arrogant ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:26.20,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hey, Applejack! How'd you like\Nto be immortalized as my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.64,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Immorta-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:32.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Are you taking notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:35.08,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yep! I've been hoof-picked\Nby Rainbow Dash herself…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:36.80,Spike,,0,0,0,,…to write her autobiography.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:41.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Um… Autobiographies are supposed to\Nbe written by the pony they are about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:44.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Maybe for your normal,\Nrun-of-the-mill ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:47.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But I'm far too busy saving lives to stop and write.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:50.36,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's why I hired Spike as my ghostwriter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:52.54,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Aaah! Spike's a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:58.98,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Spike here writes down everything I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:05:59.95,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Don't you, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:03.67,Spike,,0,0,0,,"Don't you, Spike?"\NGot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:09.76,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,This way I can stay focused on performing those acts of bravery\Nthat nopony else has the guts to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:13.65,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it takes guts. But it also takes brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:16.10,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And sometimes a big lunch and a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:20.92,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Being a hero is surely not for everypony\Nbut I'm up to the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:29.20,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,'ere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:33.26,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Someday I wanna be just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:36.04,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Aim high, kid, but don't\Naim for the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:41.51,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Help! Heeelp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:44.60,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Uh… Don't you think you should go and help?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:48.63,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. I've got a good ten seconds\Nto spare. Just a couple more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:57.04,Spike,,0,0,0,,"The tension is unbearable."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.66,Spike,,0,0,0,,"Will Rainbow Dash make it on time?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:21.60,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Holy turnips! That pony came out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:24.22,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I've never seen such bravery in all my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:27.91,Mayor,,0,0,0,,That's right. Ponyville has a new hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:33.10,Mayor,,0,0,0,,A mysterious mare, that has\Ndone well by our fair city today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:37.91,Mayor,,0,0,0,,I dub this new masked hero\Nthe Mysterious Mare Do Well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:42.35,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Mare Do Well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:45.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well, that mare would do well to stay out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:50.60,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Ponyville's only got room for one hero and that hero is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:11.41,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Never fear! Your friendly neighborhood Rainbow…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:15.91,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Do you think you could skip your catchphrase\Nand just hurry up and save us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:18.87,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Ugh… Fine. Picky, picky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:45.09,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you, Mare Do… Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:50.84,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it! Mare Do Well is stronger than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:57.18,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well, a hero is more than just muscle. And she's gonna learn that the hard way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.15,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Never fear, your friendly neighbor…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.68,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Never fear…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:35.87,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:38.09,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:39.55,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:11.08,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Look out for the… Watch out for falling…\NWatch your left! Left!Your other left!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:15.24,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Here you go. Safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:25.11,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well, Mare Do Well, or should I call you Mare Do Slow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:29.80,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You're gonna have to pick up the pace,\Nif you wanna compete with me cause I move like lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:34.08,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Actually, she saved all of us.\NWe owe her our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:48.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Okay. She's strong, fast and somehow\Nknows what's gonna happen ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:50.58,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I gotta step up my game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:05.07,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,If the dam breaks, the whole town will be flooded!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:07.55,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Looks like Ponyville needs a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:13.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Easy-peasy. My game is officially back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:16.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,If only somepony were here to pat me on the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:18.33,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Huh. Guess I'll have to do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:26.20,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Heeelp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:39.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:43.08,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Huh. I *suppose* you want me to thank…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:55.39,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:12.39,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Let me get this straight. She's strong, she's agile… and she's magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.92,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,How do I compete with THAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:23.67,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. I do have a leg up on her. And that leg is…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:25.51,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:29.82,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Ha! Take that, Mare Do Well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:40.73,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, for the love of Pete…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:47.85,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Gotta hand it to the girl.\NThat Mare Do Well sure can pull out\Nsome pretty pretty heroic feats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:52.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I must say I was impressed by that spell she used to fix the dam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:55.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Seems like something like that\Nwould take quite a bit of study.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:13:00.57,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,She really cares about everypony's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:04.06,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Have you seen her costume?\NIt is to die for!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:06.35,Rarity,,0,0,0,,If you ask me, she's a hero of fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:08.76,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And she's modest and humble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:11.03,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,She lets her actions speak for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:12.60,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Gotta admire that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:16.41,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I don't have to admire that! I don't think she's all that great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:18.19,Spike,,0,0,0,,"She's great."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.35,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:21.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sounds like somepony's jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.13,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Who? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:24.82,Spike,,0,0,0,,"Rainbow Dash is jealous."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Don't write that, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:34.03,Spike,,0,0,0,,"Correction: Rainbow Dash is very jealous."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:36.06,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Fine! Laugh all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:40.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But I'll be the one laughing when I prove\Nto you all that I'm just as good…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:43.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,…no, that I'm a better hero than Mare Do Well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:54.28,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No sign of trouble here, darn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:13:58.59,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Buses and baby carriages are always careening down this hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:01.31,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Where is an out-of-control vehicle when you need one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:06.47,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,There are absolutely no freak natural\Ndisasters going on anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:10.56,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to prove myself\Nwhen everything's so normal and safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:15.59,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there, Granny Smith! You don't have to pretend with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.59,0:14:18.34,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I can see you're way\Nover your head here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:20.37,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Yes, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:25.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You're putting on a brave face! I get it.\NBut you don't have to anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.19,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'll help you cross the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.75,0:14:32.03,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Actually, I can cross the street just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:37.93,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! You're in extremely capable hooves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:43.03,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,Stop! Back off! Back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:49.74,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Here we are! Safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:54.79,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,A good and heroic citizen deserves a little recognition. Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:15:00.18,GrannySmith,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to cross the street in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.43,0:15:07.09,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Somepony's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You'd better let me handle this, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:16.15,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,For your own safety I must\Nask you to stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:17.81,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:40.40,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:43.87,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Uh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:45.86,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,How would you describe what I just did?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:47.84,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Would you say I was… amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:49.80,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Aren't you milking this a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:53.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Please, just answer the question. Was I or was I not amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:56.27,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're amazing, all right. An amazingly…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:57.49,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:09.68,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Another great feat of heroism. I have just saved that grass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:11.27,Somepony,,0,0,0,,From what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:16.14,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,From weeds! Weeds that were attempting to eat this lawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:19.05,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:21.58,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:25.74,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, who am I kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:37.51,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,All anypony talks about is Mare Do Well this and Mare Do Well that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:39.00,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:42.10,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,How could everypony forget about me so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:45.38,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I mean, have I changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:47.29,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Same sleek body…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:48.83,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Same flowing mane…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:50.90,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Same spectacular hooves…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:53.28,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Nope! I'm still awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:55.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,They're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:59.12,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But… then why am I all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:02.33,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I hate being all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:04.63,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:06.24,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:09.00,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No need to apologize, squirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:11.14,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Anypony could make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:13.35,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Mistake? What mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:17.01,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:18.85,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,To invite you to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:23.98,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,We're heading off to the thank you parade for Ponyville's greatest hero: Mare Do Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:27.52,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No! No way! Can't you see I…\NI wanna be alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:29.60,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I love being alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:32.32,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Oh. Okay. See you later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:35.15,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right. Like I'm gonna thank {\i1}her{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:38.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mare Do Well, whoever you are, for ruining e…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:42.16,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hey, squirt! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.82,0:17:48.36,Mayor,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Ponyville's first, but surely not last…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:52.06,Mayor,,0,0,0,,…thank you parade in honor of our city's greatest hero, the Mysterious…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:56.60,Mayor,,0,0,0,,…Mare Do Well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:04.66,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,The Mysterious Mare Do Well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:10.66,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So what are you hiding? Let's see how mysterious you are without that mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:35.94,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What a hay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:58.97,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I got you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:05.65,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,All right, Miss Mysterious. Mystery…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:08.09,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,…solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:10.78,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,P-P-P-P-Pinkie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:21.72,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Twilight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:25.59,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Applejack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:27.96,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,There were three of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:31.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yep. We all played Mare Do Well at different times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:34.08,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I stopped the carriage bus with these babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:36.94,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Bucky McGillicuddy and Kicks McGee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:39.90,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I saved the construction workers with my Pinkie sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:45.09,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:46.06,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:48.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And I used my magic to fix the dam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:51.99,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Ooh! And I did the flyby afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.99,0:19:53.41,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I made the costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:55.74,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Fabulous if I do say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:20:02.43,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I don't understand. Why?!\NDon't you want me to be a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:05.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Of course we want you to be a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:07.84,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But a real hero doesn't brag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:11.24,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Uh, I guess I did start to brag a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:13.24,Somepony,,0,0,0,,A LITTLE?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:15.93,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Okay, a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:19.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Celebrating your accomplishments is natural, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:22.30,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Rubbin' them in everypony's face is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:26.99,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Yeah! The only thing that should be rubbed\Nin anypony's face is chocolate cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.36,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I think we're gettin' off topic here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:38.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What we're trying to say is it's great to be really good at something…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:41.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…but it's important to act with grace and humility.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:46.99,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh! That makes loads more sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:49.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:54.57,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And I guess I should also act with grace\Nand humility when others outshine me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:56.68,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Like… Mare Do Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:21:00.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you've got a letter to write to Princess Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:01.85,Spike,,0,0,0,,Already got it covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:04.97,Spike,,0,0,0,,As your ghostwriter, I've already penned a letter to the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:09.11,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's nice of you, Spike, but I really wanna write this letter myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:13.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on! I wrote the whole thing already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:15.24,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:17.74,Spike,,0,0,0,,"Dear Princess Cel…"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:20.14,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Look out! It's a real ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:35.06,Somepony,,0,0,0,,SCHASTLIVYI PONETC
